250
00:29:25,984 --> 00:29:27,528
The white coat.

251
00:29:29,696 --> 00:29:31,031
So I see.

252
00:29:32,074 --> 00:29:34,409
I'm Larry. The doctor.

253
00:29:34,743 --> 00:29:36,036
Hello, Dr. Larry.

254
00:29:36,078 --> 00:29:39,039
Feel free to call me "The Sultan."

255
00:29:44,878 --> 00:29:47,840
I can't believe these things actually happen.

256
00:29:48,215 --> 00:29:50,676
I thought if you showed up,
you'd be an old trout.

257
00:29:50,759 --> 00:29:53,637
