258
00:29:54,596 --> 00:29:56,223
Well, thank you.

259
00:29:58,350 --> 00:30:01,145
Fish. You gotta respect them.

260
00:30:02,479 --> 00:30:04,314
- Have you?
- Of course.

261
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:07,526
We were fish. Long ago.

262
00:30:07,943 --> 00:30:09,820
Before we were apes.

263
